Class IntegerNumber

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.nec.nle.siafu.types.IntegerNumber
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Publishable

    public class IntegerNumber
extends Object
implements Publishable
    This Publishable encapsulates an int primitive and makes it serializable (it can be flattened and blown up again) for use with Siafu.
    Author:
    Miquel Martin
